\c 40
\s Mhinduro yaJobho
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakapindura Jobho ndokuti\x + 38.1.\x*:
\p
\v 2 Anopikisana neWemasimbaose anga\add mu\add*raira here? Anoshoora Mwari ngaapindure\x + 33.13.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Zvino Jobho wakapindura Jehovha ndokuti:
\p
\v 4 Tarirai, ndakaderera; ndingakupindurai chii\x + 42.6. Nah. 1.14. Ezi. 9.6.\x*? Ruoko rwangu ndaisa pamuromo wangu\x + Map. 39.9. Vato. 18.19.\x*.
\v 5 Ndakataura kamwe, asi handingapinduri\x + 9.3. Map. 62.11.\x*; hongu kaviri, asi handingaendereri mberi\x + 9.3. Map. 62.11.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Jehovha wakapindura Jobho kubva muchamupupuri ndokuti\x + 38.1.\x*:
\p
\v 7 Sunga chiuno chako ikozvino semurume\x + 38.3.\x*; ndichakubvunza, zvino uchandizivisa\x + 38.3. 42.4.\x*.
\v 8 Uchaparadza mutongo wangu here\x + Map. 51.4. VaRom. 3.4. Map. 50.21.\x*? Ungandirasa kuti uve wakarurama here\x + 32.2. 35.2.\x*?
\v 9 Uye une ruoko saMwari here? Kana ungatinhira nenzwi here saiye\x + 37.4.\x*?
\v 10 Ikozvino zvishongedze neukuru nerukudzo; uye uzvipfekedze neruremekedzo nekubwinya\x + Map. 104.1. Map. 93.1.\x*.
\v 11 Paradzira hasha dzekutsamwa kwako\x + 21.30.\x*, ugotarisa wose anozvikudza, ugomuninipisa\x + Isa. 2.12. Dhan. 4.37.\x*.
\v 12 Tarira wose anozvikudza\x + Isa. 2.12. Dhan. 4.37.\x*, umuderedze\x + Isa. 2.12. Dhan. 4.37.\x*. Zvino tsikira pasi vakaipa panzvimbo yavo\x + 36.20.\x*.
\v 13 Uvavige pamwe chete\x + Isa. 2.10.\x* paguruva\x + Isa. 2.10.\x*\x + 17.16. 21.26.\x*; sunga zviso zvavo pakavanda.
\v 14 Zvino ipapo ndichareurura kwauri, kuti ruoko rwako rwerudyi rungakuponesa\x + Map. 98.1. Isa. 59.16. 63.5.\x*.
\v 15 Tarira hako mvuu, yandakaita pamwe newe; inodya uswa senzombe\x + Map. 104.14.\x*.
\v 16 Tarira hako, simba rayo riri muchiuno chayo; uye kugwinya kwayo kuri pamakakava edumbu rayo.
\v 17 Inotsvikidza muswe wayo semusidhari; marunda ezvidya zvayo akarukwa-rukwa\x + Marir. 1.14.\x*.
\v 18 Mapfupa ayo ipombi dzendarira; mbabvu dzayo dzakaita semazariro ematare.
\v 19 Ndiyo yekutanga\x + Amo. 6.1,6. Zvir. 8.22.\x* yenzira dzaMwari\x + 26.14.\x*; muiti wayo anoswededza munondo wayo.
\v 20 Nokuti makomo anoivigira zvekudya, panotamba mhuka dzose dzesango.
\v 21 Inorara pasi pemiti yemirotusi, pakavanda petsanga nepaguvi\x + 8.11 Eze. 47.11.\x*.
\v 22 Miti yemirotusi inoifukidza \add ne\add*mumvuri wayo; mikonachando yerukova inoipoteredza\x + Rev. 23.40. Map. 137.2. Isa. 15.7. 44.4.\x*.
\v 23 Tarira, rwizi rwunomanikidza, haikurumidzi\x + Det. 20.3.\x*; ine chivimbo kunyange Joridhani rwuchibudira kumuromo wayo\x + 38.8.\x*.
\v 24 \add Pane\add* angaibata here nemeso ayo? Angaibaya mhino nemusungo?